# 
def user_description(df, col_reg, region):
    try:
        #      
        pivot_plat = (df
                      .pivot_table(
                          index='platform', 
                          values=col_reg, 
                          aggfunc='sum')
                      .sort_values(by=col_reg, ascending=False)
                     )
        
        #   ()
        plat = (pivot_plat
                .head()
                .append(pd.DataFrame(
                    data={col_reg:[pivot_plat
                      .sort_values(by=col_reg, ascending=False)
                            [-(len(pivot_plat.index)-5):][col_reg].sum()]}, 
                    index=['']))
               )
        
        #    
        plat.plot(
            kind='pie',
            y=col_reg,
            title=f'      {region}',
            label='',
            autopct='%0.1f%%',
            colors=colors,
            figsize=(5,5),
            legend=False)
                
        # -5 
        plt.figure(figsize=(14,2))
        plt.barh(
            (plat
                .head()
                .sort_values(by=col_reg)
                .index
            ), 
            (plat
                .head()
                .sort_values(by=col_reg)
                [col_reg]
            )
                
        );
        plt.grid(True)
        plt.ylabel('')
        plt.xlabel(', ')
        plt.title(f'-5     {region}')
        plt.show()
        
        
        #                   
        pivot_genres = (df
                      .pivot_table(
                          index='genre', 
                          values=col_reg, 
                          aggfunc='sum')
                      .sort_values(by=col_reg, ascending=False)
                     )
        
        
        #   ()
        genres = (pivot_genres
                .head()
                .append(pd.DataFrame(
                    data={col_reg:[pivot_genres
                      .sort_values(by=col_reg, ascending=False)
                            [-(len(pivot_genres.index)-5):][col_reg].sum()]}, 
                    index=['']))
               )
        
        #    
        genres.plot(
            kind='pie',
            y=col_reg,
            title=f'       {region}',
            label='',
            autopct='%0.1f%%',
            colors=colors,
            figsize=(5,5),
            legend=False)
                
        # -5 
        plt.figure(figsize=(14,2))
        plt.barh(
            (genres
                .head()
                .sort_values(by=col_reg)
                .index
            ), 
            (genres
                .head()
                .sort_values(by=col_reg)
                [col_reg]
            )
                
        );
        plt.grid(True)
        plt.ylabel('')
        plt.xlabel(', ')
        plt.title(f'-5     {region}')
        plt.show()       
        
        #                   
        pivot_rating = (df
                      .pivot_table(
                          index='rating', 
                          values=col_reg, 
                          aggfunc='sum')
                      .sort_values(by=col_reg, ascending=False)
                     )
        
        #:     
        pivot_rating.plot(
            kind='pie',
            y=col_reg,
            title=f'       {region}',
            label='',
            autopct='%0.1f%%',
            colors=colors,
            figsize=(5,5),
            legend=False)
    
    except:
        return('   user_description')
